        '\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eJoin our family at Pricefx, a \u003c/span\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eleading SaaS Pricing\u003c/strong\u003e\u003cspan\u003e (Price Optimization \u0026amp; Management) and CPQ (Configure-Price-Quote) vendor. Experiencing consistent annual growth, Pricefx remains committed to \u003c/span\u003e\u003cstrong\u003estable employment\u003c/strong\u003e\u003cspan\u003e. We value flexibility and provide home office and remote work opportunities. Our product boasts \u003c/span\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eoutstanding customer reviews\u003c/strong\u003e\u003cspan\u003e ranging from small companies to renowned names such as \u003c/span\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMichelin, Sonoco, Danone\u003c/strong\u003e\u003cspan\u003e, \u003c/span\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eAvery Dennison\u003c/strong\u003e\u003cspan\u003e, and \u003c/span\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eBosch\u003c/strong\u003e\u003cspan\u003e.\u003c/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eWith branches in 7 countries and over 30 nationalities, Pricefx is a \u003c/span\u003e\u003cstrong\u003egenuinely international\u003c/strong\u003e\u003cspan\u003e and \u003c/span\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ediverse company\u003c/strong\u003e\u003cspan\u003e, fostering a warm, welcoming, and respectful environment. Join us at Pricefx and be part of a winning team that values your unique contributions, encourages accountability and personal growth, and celebrates collective achievements.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch4\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eYour mission\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eBecoming a Technical Trainer in Pricefx means to accept full focus on the quality of our pricing platform. You will work closely with the whole Pricefx delivery team as well as with project consultants and other stakeholders, you will organize your work your way, set priorities and of course, you will train a lot. \u003c/p\u003e\u003ch4\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eYou will be in charge of...\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePreparing and delivering live, instructor-led training targeted to Pricefx stakeholders (at the lo\u003cspan\u003ecation or remotely).\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMaintaining and updating both Pricefx and tooling skills.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCollaborating with the Product Education team on product topics and content alignment.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAssisting in creating, updating, and maintaining Pricefx training content \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAssisting with Pricefx education and product adoption projects\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSupporting the development of new training and collaborating with cross-functional teams\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\u003ch4\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhat should you have to succeed?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eProgramming experience is a must.\u003c/strong\u003e You will have to write the code for education purposes up to 20-30% of the time (coding is not product-related). We use Groovy, but you will learn how to use it fast, in case you already have a solid knowledge of \u003cstrong\u003eJAVA\u003c/strong\u003e/similar programming language.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eExperience with \u003cstrong\u003eSQL \u003c/strong\u003eand database knowledge is a must. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eExperience creating technical documentation or learning content from topics ranging from user guides to APIs is required.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAbility to resolve problems and think outside the box for solutions. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAbility to work independently.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eA natural curiosity for technology.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eExperience in creating and delivering training in a corporate environment (both in-person and remotely), ideally in the field of IT - software and tools.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eWillingness to travel up to 10-15% of the time.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAbility to speak \u003cstrong\u003eEnglish\u003c/strong\u003e fluently (written and communication skills at \u003cstrong\u003eB2+ level or higher are required\u003c/strong\u003e)\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\u003ch4\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eLocation\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003ePrague, Hradec Králové, Ostrava, or any location in the Czech Republic\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003ch4\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eOther specifics...\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eApplicants need to have \u003cstrong\u003evalid permission to live and work in the Czech Republic\u003c/strong\u003e (we do not provide any assistance with work permit transcripts)\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eWe offer a full-time employment contract\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eWe require a clean criminal record\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\u003ch4\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhat will you love about us?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eOur employees appreciate the warm and friendly atmosphere, as well as the flexibility and growth opportunities we provide. Check out our \u003ca href="https://www.glassdoor.com/Overview/Working-at-Pricefx-EI_IE1879589.11,18.htmscore"\u003eGlassdoor\u003c/a\u003e \u0026amp; \u003ca href="https://www.atmoskop.cz/en/nazory-na-zamestnavatele/2949899-price-f-x-s-r-o"\u003eAtmoskop\u003c/a\u003e scores and reviews.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eWe will support your home office setup with a monthly IT allowance. We prioritize work-life balance and, in addition to vacation, offer work anniversary, birthday, and CSR days off. Building a sense of community is important. We organize regular virtual or in-person meetups and many social activities and challenges.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWe’re proud also to offer some amazing benefits:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eWe will allow you to bring your own working equipment by providing an \u003cstrong\u003eoption of a monthly allowance\u003c/strong\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e (3825 \u003c/strong\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCZK Net\u003c/strong\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e)\u003c/strong\u003e instead of pre-selected working tools (laptop and cell phone)\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eWe provide \u003cstrong\u003e1750 \u003c/strong\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCZK in Benefit points\u003c/strong\u003e, which can be used for culture, travel, or sports (Multisport card)\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003e25\u003c/strong\u003e days off, \u003cstrong\u003e3\u003c/strong\u003e free/sick days, \u003cstrong\u003e2\u003c/strong\u003e CSR days, and \u003cstrong\u003e1\u003c/strong\u003e additional day off during your birthday month\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eOur offices are exceptional in look and atmosphere, but \u003cstrong\u003eyou can also work from home or in a park\u003c/strong\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eA great work-life balance, where you can work full-time on a flexible schedule\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003eBefore you apply please visit the link below, read GDPR information and give us your consent with data processing.\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href="https://pricefx.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/UNI/pages/589561897/GDPR+Information+for+Candidates+-+JobScore"\u003eGDPR for candidates\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e',
